  "table-8-3": (
    caption: [Categories of Memories and Major Brain Regions Involved. This table distinguishes between different memory types: short-term/working memory (短期记忆/工作记忆) involving prefrontal cortex; declarative/explicit memory (陈述性记忆/外显记忆) including episodic and semantic memory involving hippocampus and temporal lobes; and procedural/implicit memory (程序性记忆/内隐记忆) for motor skills involving basal nuclei, cerebellum, and motor cortex.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
