  "table-8-4": (
    caption: [Principal Ascending Tracts of Spinal Cord (主要上行传导束). This table lists sensory pathways carrying different modalities: fasciculus gracilis and fasciculus cuneatus (薄束和楔束) for discriminative touch and proprioception; lateral and anterior spinothalamic tracts (脊髓丘脑束) for pain, temperature, and crude touch; spinocerebellar tracts (脊髓小脑束) for unconscious proprioception to cerebellum.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
