  "table-8-5": (
    caption: [Descending Motor Tracts to Spinal Interneurons and Motor Neurons (下行运动传导束). This table categorizes motor pathways: pyramidal tracts (锥体束) including lateral and anterior corticospinal tracts for voluntary movement; extrapyramidal tracts (锥体外系) including rubrospinal (红核脊髓束), tectospinal (顶盖脊髓束), vestibulospinal (前庭脊髓束), and reticulospinal (网状脊髓束) tracts for posture and involuntary movements.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
