  "table-8-6": (
    caption: [Summary of Cranial Nerves (脑神经). Complete listing of all 12 pairs of cranial nerves (I-XII) with their names, types (sensory, motor, or mixed), and primary functions. Examples include: I Olfactory (嗅神经, sensory for smell), II Optic (视神经, sensory for vision), III Oculomotor (动眼神经, motor for eye movement), V Trigeminal (三叉神经, mixed for facial sensation and chewing), VII Facial (面神经, mixed for facial expression and taste), X Vagus (迷走神经, mixed for visceral functions).],
